titleInfo.title: List of Chiefs within the Rajpootana [Rﾄ）asthﾄ］] Agency

mods.abstract: Printed list of all the Chiefs within the Rajpootana [Rﾄ）asthﾄ］] Agency. The list is taken from volume III of an unknown publication.The verso of the folio has a pencil note stating that the list has been sent to Pelly with Thornton's (Thomas Henry Thornton?) compliments and that the Chiefs are not listed in any fixed order of precedence, as although the question was taken up it had never been settled.
